eight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tu\u1ea7n qua, nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n v\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u lan t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0 ra \u0111\u1ebfn to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u0129nh h\u1eb1ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-roma-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183963.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">AS Roma chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 v\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona</span></span> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Juventus su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c ngay t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau, Salzburg vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Roma khi lo\u1ea1i Lazio kh\u1ecfi Europa League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tu tran hoa cua Arsenal Dung dua voi nhung ke cung duong! hinh anh\" title=\"T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/musa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal su\u00fdt n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Danny Welbeck. Hay n\u00f3i theo c\u00e1ch v\u0103n hoa h\u01a1n, &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&quot; Wenger x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 quan khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o s\u00e2n VEB Arena. Ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal &quot;gi\u00e3&quot; cho 4-1 t\u1ea1i Emirates m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n kh\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Ngay trong ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, CSKA Moscow ch\u1eb3ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi Chalov m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i su\u1ed1t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb rang tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc ch\u1ea3o n\u00f3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Nababkin nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</span></span>, CSKA d\u1ed3n l\u00ean c\u00f2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal trong \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00fac \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &quot;Barcelona phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2&quot;, theo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Welbeck.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran hoa cua Arsenal khien thay tro Wenger tho phao nhe nhom.\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/ars-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u00fat xa \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i s\u00e1t s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Ignashevich d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 h\u1ed3i chu\u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh, \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot;. Arsenal ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 4 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 tan ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow. Welbeck t\u1eeb pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t - hai v\u1edbi Elneny tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1! CSKA Moscow l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i sau b\u00e0n thua \u1ea5y, ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u n\u00e0o n\u1eefa, Arsenal v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y Arsene Wenger c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5m m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng hay... b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn Europa League \u0111\u00eam qua, c\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u1ec1u thu v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Arsenal h\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda, Atletico thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Leipzig thua th\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Marseille r\u1ed3i m\u1ea5t v\u00e9. Th\u1ea3m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Lazio, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 4-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i thua Salzburg 1-4 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u00fai cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ngoai tran hoa cua Arsenal, Salzburg cung lam nen mot cu soc khac tai dau truong chau Au.\" title=\"Ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Salzburg c\u0169ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Salzburg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Salzburg c\u0169ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barcelona hay Real Madrid c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. M\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u0103ng, khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb l\u00e9p v\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1? Kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng... b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn t\u00e2m l\u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 HLV Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal. Khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u1eefng Barca, Real Madrid, Arsenal hay Lazio \u0111\u1ec1u \u00edt hay nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u00e1i v\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u00eau hao, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 khi thua l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Roma, Juventus, Salzburg hay CSKA Moscow nh\u01b0 con th\u00fa b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0m v\u1ed1n v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t b\u00ean \u0111ang hoang mang lo s\u1ee3, xu\u1ed1ng tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00ean ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng &quot;c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n&quot; m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u00edt ng\u00e0y qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-Moscow-2-2-(3-6)-Arsenal-Hoa-nguoc,-Phao-thu-ghi-ten-vao-ban-ket-hinh-anh-goc-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-hung-danny-welbeck-cho-biet-arsenal-khong-thoai-mai-172-184128.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan-184-184127.html\">H\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda CSKA Moscow, HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-cska-moskva-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-tu-ket-europa-league-201718-184-184122.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 CSKA Moskva vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\">CSKA Moscow 2-2 (3-6) Arsenal: H\u00f2a ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/wenger-lay-barca-lam-bai-hoc-canh-tinh-arsenal-184-184086.html\">Wenger l\u1ea5y Barca l\u00e0m b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-2h05-ngay-134-lieu-co-dia-chan-184-184081.html\">CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal (2h05 ng\u00e0y 13/4): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1114","checkdouble":"184129"},{"date":"07:02 13/04","title":"Salzburg 4-1 (6-5) Lazio: K\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \"nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u\" n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00c1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/salzburg-41-65-lazio-ky-tich-cua-nhuoc-tieu-nuoc-ao.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5