er; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban ket Europa League Ky tich tu ke that bai hinh anh\" title=\"B\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League K\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1eeb k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/bon-doi-lot-vao-ban-ket-europa-league-ky-tich-tu-ga-nhuoc-tieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>B\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 Atletico (2-0), Leipzig (1-0) v\u00e0 Lazio (4-2) \u0111\u1ec1u thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Atletico thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sporting CP nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 (2-1). Nh\u01b0ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leipzig thua \u0111\u1ebfn 2-5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Marseille, qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3-5 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. \"\u0110\u1eafng\" nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Lazio khi h\u1ecd thua \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00c1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \"nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u\" Salzburg v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-4, qua \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-6.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League l\u00e0 Arsenal, Atletico Madrid, Marseille v\u00e0 Salzburg. L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 18h00 ng\u00e0y 13/4 (chi\u1ec1u nay).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u00e0i n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal (Anh)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng theo UEFA: 9</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb: V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t: Ramsey (4)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Atletico Madrid (T\u00e2y Ban Nha)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng theo UEFA: 3</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb: V\u00f2ng 32 \u0111\u1ed9i (r\u1edbt xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb Champions League)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t: Saul, Griezmann (3)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Marseille (Ph\u00e1p)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng theo UEFA: 57</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb: V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t: Ocampos (4)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Salzburg (\u00c1o)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng theo UEFA: 33</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb: V\u00f2ng play-off Champions League</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t: Berisha, Dabbur (5)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Europa League t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/marseille-52-53-leipzig-tam-quan-trong-cua-kinh-nghiem-184-184132.html\">Marseille 5-2 (5-3) Leipzig: T\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salzburg-41-65-lazio-ky-tich-cua-nhuoc-tieu-nuoc-ao-184-184130.html\">Salzburg 4-1 (6-5) Lazio: K\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00c1o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan-184-184127.html\">H\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda CSKA Moscow, HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\">CSKA Moscow 2-2 (3-6) Arsenal: H\u00f2a ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/wenger-lay-barca-lam-bai-hoc-canh-tinh-arsenal-184-184086.html\">Wenger l\u1ea5y Barca l\u00e0m b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nhan-tin-soc-tu-chan-thuong-cua-mkhitaryan-172-183888.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin s\u1ed1c t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1112","checkdouble":"184131"},{"date":"07:10 13/04","title":"Marseille 5-2 (5-3) Leipzig: T\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kinh nghi\u1ec7m","type":"B\u00f3ng 