, 255);\">CSKA Moscow 2-2  Arsenal</span></span>.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Laurent Koscielny minh oan cho Wenger ve chien thuat tran gap CSKA Moscow.\" title=\"Laurent Koscielny minh oan cho Wenger v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CSKA Moscow.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/koscielny-minh-oan-cho-wenger-sau-tran-hoa-cska-moscow.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Laurent Koscielny minh oan cho Wenger v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CSKA Moscow.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>D\u00f9 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y v\u1eabn gi\u00fap Arsenal l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bon-doi-lot-vao-ban-ket-europa-league-ky-tich-tu-ga-nhuoc-tieu-184-184131.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</span></span> v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1  6-3 nh\u01b0ng HLV Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd  ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Arsenal ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap CSKA Moscow  c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh nguy hi\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Koscielny minh oan cho Wenger</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger, trung v\u1ec7 Laurent Koscielny cho  bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 ra. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t  qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng  \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y&quot;.</p>\r\n<p>&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c pha tranh ch\u1ea5p. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, s\u1edf h\u1eefu  nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ghi  th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadt vui khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea5y  l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t&quot;.</p>\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Wenger c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan khi\u1ebfn Arsenal thi \u0111\u1ea5u  kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i Koscielny minh oan cho Wenger, m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Danny  Welbeck tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi thi  \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tu-tran-hoa-cua-arsenal-dung-dua-voi-nhung-ke-cung-duong-184-184129.html\">T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal: \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-hung-danny-welbeck-cho-biet-arsenal-khong-thoai-mai-172-184128.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck: Arsenal h\u00f2a