ner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sporting Lisbon trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n song \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa chan thuong sau tran Sporting 1-0 Atletico hinh anh\" title=\"Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn Sporting 1-0 Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Diego-Costa-chan-thuong-sau-tran-Sporting-1-0-Atletico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico Madrid v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Simeone \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 tung ra 9 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong \u0111\u00f3 2 tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh, qu\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh con s\u1ed1 17 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 7 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng Sporting ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Fredy Montero. Thua tr\u1eadn 0-1 nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/atletico-madrid-1390.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atletico Madrid</strong></span> v\u1eabn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Salzburg, Arsenal v\u00e0 Marseille.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico Madrid tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft. Theo \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/diego-costa-44297.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Diego Costa</strong></span> ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 52, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Fernando Torres.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa chan thuong\" title=\"Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/atletico-madrid-tra-gia-cuc-dat-sau-tam-ve-vao-ban-ket-europa-league.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Costa d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i, Atletico c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u bao l\u00e2u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone th\u00ec ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 \u0111au, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Costa ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Atletico c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Lucas Hernandez, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 46. N\u1ebfu b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Atletico.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed9 ba Nicolas Gaitan, Augusto Fernandez v\u00e0 Yannick Carrasco t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/21212-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1109","checkdouble":"184139"},{"date":"21:06 12/04","title":"CSKA Moscow 2-2 (3-6) Arsenal: H\u00f2a ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/ket-qua-cska-moskva-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-tu-ket-europa-league-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;