. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n  \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chalov ghi ban mo ti so cho CSKA Moscow.\" title=\"Chalov ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho CSKA Moscow.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/chalov.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Chalov ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CSKA Moskva vs Arsenal.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CSKA Moskva vs Arsenal di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u00edt t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Arsenal kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i an  to\u00e0n, trong khi CSKA thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 &quot;s\u1eafc&quot;. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 39, t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t  ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf cho CSKA Moskva khi Chalov \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Nababkin.Nhen l\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CSKA Moskva trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i  hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t,  t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moskva vs Arsenal l\u00e0 1-0 t\u1ea1m nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<p>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n, CSKA Moskva ch\u01a1i hay v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1  h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Ph\u00fat 53, Golovin c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  Cech. Sau hai b\u00e0n thua, Arsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 &quot;th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh&quot; khi t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 69, Koscielny tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ph\u00fat 71,  t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 su\u00fdt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 3-0 khi Ignashevic tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat xa \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i s\u00e1t  c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Welbeck ghi ban giai cuu Arsenal.\" title=\"Danny Welbeck ghi b\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Arsenal.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/welbeck-1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Danny Welbeck ghi b\u00e0n &quot;gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u&quot; Arsenal.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhen nh\u00f3m cho CSKA Moskva \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh. Welbeck  d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng t\u1eeb pha ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a Elneny ph\u00fat 76 \u0111em l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-2 cho  Arsenal.</p>\r\n<p>CSKA Moskva sau b\u00e0n thua kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, trong khi  Arsenal l\u1ea1i nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Ph\u00fat 88. Iwobi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i  \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Ozil nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.</p>\r\n<p>Welbeck trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n  nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Akinfeev. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat sau t\u1eeb pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng  nhanh, Ramsey ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho Arsenal.</p>\r\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CSKA Moskva vs Arsenal kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-2, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2  Arsene Wenger ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/ket-qua-cska-moskva-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-tu-ket-europa-league-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\">CSKA Moscow 2-2 (3-6) Arsenal: H\u00f2a ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League 2017/18 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong \u00e2u lo khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\