u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, Juventus l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0. Do l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng 3-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Real, n\u1ebfu t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean, hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Michael Oliver x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Mehdi Benatia c\u1ee7a Juventus ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Lucas Vazquez trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. M\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty cho Real v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Juve \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon n\u1ed5i xung. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Del Piero phat bieu ve Buffon voi su khong dong y hinh anh\" title=\"Del Piero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Buffon v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Del-Piero-phat-bieu-ve-Buffon-voi-su-khong-dong-y-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Buffon ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, Cristiano Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n gi\u00fap Real l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League d\u00f9 thua 1-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buffon kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver</strong></span> th\u1eadm t\u1ec7. Anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i g\u1ecdi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver l\u00e0 \u201ck\u1ebb s\u00e1t nh\u00e2n\u201d v\u00e0 \u201ckh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Del Piero kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Alessandro Del Piero, anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Del Piero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Buffon l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-phan-ung-trong-tai-tran-real-vs-juventus-co-the-thong-cam-duoc-184-184079.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Allegri cho r\u1eb1ng Buffon c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m</strong></span>. \u201cKhi Gigi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, t\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed5i\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 9 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho Juventus (1993 t\u1edbi 2012) n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sport Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Buffon va Allegri\" title=\"thu mon Buffon va Allegri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/thu-mon-Buffon-va-Allegri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Del Piero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Buffon v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Gigi l\u1ea1i d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n t\u00edch hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh n\u00f3i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00fang.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juventus thua chung cu\u1ed9c Real 3-4</strong></span> v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 \u00f4m h\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m qua. Th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bianconeri t\u1eebng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nga-mu-truoc-nhung-chien-binh-cua-allegri-184-184090.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus: Ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh c\u1ee7a Allegri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real 1-3 Juventus: H\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div 