s/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates, Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m n\u1eeda chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-cska-moscow-vs-arsenal-02h05-ngay-134-europa-league-201718-372-184121.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"> tr\u00ean s\u00e2n VEB Arena l\u1ea1i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Arsene Wenger thua nhan Arsenal da mang tam ly chu quan.\" title=\"HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 quan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 quan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng CSKA Moscow b\u1ea5t ch\u1ee3t v\u00f9ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, c\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Fedor Chalov v\u00e0 Kirill Nababkin. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Europa League khi\u1ebfn Arsenal &quot;th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck v\u00e0 Aaron Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 &quot;gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u&quot; Arsenal kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i VEB Arena. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y gi\u00fap &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HLV Arsene Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t&quot; - HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean BT Sports: &quot;H\u1ecd ghi hai b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Ignashevich c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t, t\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;&quot;Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Khi chuy\u1ec3n sang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. B\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat xa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec h\u01a1n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Khi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 2-1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1eafng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh th\u1ee9 5 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Fulham (2009/10), Liverpool (2009/10 v\u00e0 2015/16), Chelsea (2012/13) v\u00e0 Man Utd (2016/17).&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-Moscow-2-2-(3-6)-Arsenal-Hoa-nguoc,-Phao-thu-ghi-ten-vao-ban-ket-hinh-anh-goc-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div cla