t 75 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguoi hung Danny Welbeck cho biet Arsenal khong thoai mai hinh anh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/nguoi-hung-danny-welbeck-cho-biet-arsenal-khong-thoai-mai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan-184-184127.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger</span></span>, ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Welbeck khi\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow suy s\u1ee5p. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Welbeck \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n, \u0111em so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi 32 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf c\u00f9ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Welbeck ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\" - ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Danny Welbeck cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 xa nh\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u00e8m t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t, anh ta ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t hai v\u1edbi Elneny v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ta. C\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008-09, Arsenal l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u0103m 2009, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-Moscow-2-2-(3-6)-Arsenal-Hoa-nguoc,-Phao-thu-ghi-ten-vao-ban-ket-hinh-anh-goc-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Danny Welbeck:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-32-southampton-ngay-danny-welbeck-cuu-roi-hang-thu-172-183832.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 3-2 Southampton: Ng\u00e0y Danny Welbeck c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cham-diem-arsenal-32-southampton-172-183828.html\">Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal 3-2 Southampton: Si\u00eau nh\u00e2n Welbeck</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-southampton-20h15-ngay-84-premier-league-201718-372-183810.html\">Arsenal 3-2 Southampton (KT): Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a sao x\u1eb9t Danny Welbeck</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/dien-sau-kiem-11m-tien-dao-welbeck-hung-du-gach-da-188-182189.html\">Di\u1ec5n s\u00e2u ki\u1ebfm 11m, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Welbeck h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee7 g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tro-cung-bay-giua-ngan-ha-wenger-van-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-184-182148.html\">Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng \u201cbay gi\u1eefa ng\u00e2n h\u00e0\u201d, Wenger v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/welbeck-su-co-mat-cua-lacazette-va-aubameyang-giup-toi-co-nhieu-dong-luc-hon-172-181972.html\">Welbeck: S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1104","checkdouble":"184128"},{"date":"03:10 13/04","title":"Barca s\u1eafp chi 600 tri\u1ec7u Euro x\u00e2y l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/barca-sap-chi-600-trieu-euro-xay-lai-san-camp-nou.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6