ps://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-183870.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City b\u1ecb Man United ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-2</strong></span> trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Premier League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Man City d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf Champions League kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi \u201cch\u1ec9\u201d 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc 6 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Gabriel Jesus phat bieu ve Man City va dong doi hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Tien-dao-Gabriel-Jesus-phat-bieu-ve-Man-City-va-dong-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City tr\u1ea3i qua 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jesus th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng. Theo ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 mau ch\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Tottenham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00fang l\u00e0m lu m\u1edd nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d, Jesus n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Manchester Evening News. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi (Liverpool). Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Gabriel Jesus\" title=\"tien dao Gabriel Jesus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tien-dao-gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai th\u00edch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-12-liverpool-song-nho-toc-do-chet-vi-toc-do-184-183994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City 1-2 Liverpool</strong></span>, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady x\u1ea3y ra, Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-khong-thay-doi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-184096.html\">Man City kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/van-gaal-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-sau-tran-thang-184-184041.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City, Liverpool v\u1eabn b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV M.U xem th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-184-184038.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-sau-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool-184-184035.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City ch\u1ec9 ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league-184-184010.html\">Thua \u0111au Liverpool, Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1101","checkdouble":"184116"},{"date":"20:40 12/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/21/ly-do-chelsea-ban-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13